TITLE: Saving a Mongoose Document to MongoDB
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to save a Mongoose document to the MongoDB database using the save() method. It uses async/await for handling the asynchronous operation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/Automattic/mongoose/blob/master/docs/index.md#2025-04-14_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
await fluffy.save();
fluffy.speak();
```

