TITLE: Updating Mongoose Document Using save()
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates how to modify a Mongoose document using JavaScript assignments and save the changes to MongoDB.
SOURCE: https://github.com/Automattic/mongoose/blob/master/docs/documents.md#2025-04-14_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
doc.name = 'foo';

// Mongoose sends an `updateOne({ _id: doc._id }, { $set: { name: 'foo' } })`
// to MongoDB.
await doc.save();
```

