TITLE: Deleting Documents with Mongoose
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to delete documents matching a specific filter using the deleteOne() method. Mongoose also provides deleteMany() for removing multiple documents.
SOURCE: https://github.com/Automattic/mongoose/blob/master/docs/models.md#2025-04-14_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
await Tank.deleteOne({ size: 'large' });
```

