TITLE: Connection Error Event Handler
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to handle errors that occur after the initial connection is established using event listeners.
SOURCE: https://github.com/Automattic/mongoose/blob/master/docs/connections.md#2025-04-14_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
mongoose.connection.on('error', err => {
  logError(err);
});
```

