TITLE: Installing Mongoose via npm
DESCRIPTION: Command to install Mongoose package using npm. This is the first step in setting up a project with Mongoose.
SOURCE: https://github.com/Automattic/mongoose/blob/master/docs/index.md#2025-04-14_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: sh
CODE:
```
npm install mongoose --save
```

