TITLE: Defining a Mongoose Schema for Kittens
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to create a simple Mongoose schema with a single property. This schema will be used to define the structure of kitten documents in the database.
SOURCE: https://github.com/Automattic/mongoose/blob/master/docs/index.md#2025-04-14_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
