TITLE: Defining Mongoose Schema with Array Types in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to define a Mongoose schema with array types using TypeScript. It shows the usage of generics to properly type the schema, model, and hydrated documents, including array subdocuments.
