TITLE: Implementing Manually Typed Query Helpers in TypeScript with Mongoose
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to implement manually typed query helpers in TypeScript using Mongoose. It includes interface definitions, schema creation, and query helper implementation with proper TypeScript typing.
