TITLE: Create Operation Error Handling in Mongoose 8
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how Mongoose 8 waits for all save operations to complete before throwing validation errors, unlike Mongoose 7 which throws immediately. This allows valid documents to be saved even when one document fails validation.
